OL,5, Money borrowed to pay for Christmas    
OL,6, could take years to repay, according to
OL,7, debt advice charity StepChange.        
OL,9,FThe charity said worries about debt had
OL,10,Fled to a surge in enquiries as soon as 
OL,11,Fthe festive season was over.           
OL,13,FIts warning comes as a poll for the BBC
OL,14,Fsuggests fears over unmanageable debt. 
OL,16,FA third of respondents to the poll who 
OL,17,Fused credit to help get through        
OL,18,FChristmas and the holiday season said  
OL,19,Fthey were not confident about their    
OL,20,Fability to repay.                      
